Package: rsd
Architecture: i386 powerpc sparc amd64 arm
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${fpc-abi:Depends}
Recommends: lcl-utils, lcl
Suggests: rsd-doc
Description: Rapid Simulator Designer - IDE and simulator core package
 RSD is a development tool that allow system designes to easily create a
 simulation tool for their design. It has a powerful, block based, view with a
 source code editor as well as a code generator and a development library.
 .
 This package contains the IDE binary executable program and data files.

Package: rsd-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: rsd, fptc-src
Description: Rapid Simulator Designer - Developer's Documentation
 RSD is a development tool that allow system designes to easily create a
 simulation tool for their design. It has a powerful, block based, view with a
 source code editor as well as a code generator and a development library.
 .
 This package contains the user documentation.
